{"tid":1394094,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"全部人同我一齊去公務員集會！","createTime":"2019-08-01T09:57:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T12:47:25.000Z","uid":133983,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5e88c5f582b47e5168fe1383921eb54e4ccd4df6","tid":1394094,"uid":133983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:57:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/01/P2019080100742.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201908%2F01%2FP2019080100742.htm&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEV3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=4a792c76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/01/P2019080100742.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母啦香港政府<br />\n警察搞撐警集會就係中立　公務員搞集會就唔撚得？？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警犬屌鳩張建宗又好撚中立?又好撚支持政府施政?<br />\n<br />\n好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n坦白講　原本有好多會出公務員都會受壓力而唔出<br />\n但我地唔可以比政府得逞<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">到時佢可能會派黑警查身份證　再事後清算</span></span><br />\n<br />\n和理非係時候全面進場<br />\n用人數、聲勢等有份去既公務員唔撚洗驚<br />\n咁叻未個撚個check曬身份證去囉<br />\n我又睇下政府係唔係咁撚威憑CCTVB既片就搵得番曬所有公務員呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌 聽日香港人 公務員集會見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5891d6eba6d4d8ea5e61cfac209f461e2a0d7f04","tid":1394094,"uid":133983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:01:33.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"79f67db69e5d505dbf18b9a1752ff666e08fe87a","tid":1394094,"uid":133983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:08:00.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"805bcb4126f29d275